{"tid":1758282,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"有感而發: 政府越硬，越嚟越多淺色會走向深黃","createTime":"2019-11-27T03:07:55.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-27T03:21:42.000Z","uid":24980,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"b25293da695fa7443c9b65f0e15d8012bf56097b","tid":1758282,"uid":24980,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T03:07:55.000Z","msg":"越唔釋出善意，越會令人覺得失望，從而令更多人死心，走上深黃之路: <br />\n<br />\n理性既人會諗，唉，普選好難㗎，上面怕香港失控。<br />\n獨立調查好難嫁，怕警察作反。<br />\n<br />\n但係咁大民意作前題下，完全唔做，甚至重盲撐，<br />\n擺明同市民打對台。<br />\n我覺得會令到香港遊離派理性既人對政府完全失望<br />\n而會令到佢地對内地反感，而走上深黃之路，甚至真係獨派。我相信有不少人真係想回復返以前果種河水不犯井水，港人高度自治，中港各自互相利用，有錢一齊搵既狀態。<br />\n<br />\n其實經過呢6個月種種既事，再區選後，政府態度依舊<br />\n我相信會越來越難收尾<br />\n<br />\n表面上短暫既平靜，係比機會政府回應<br />\n大家記得10月1日前，都有一段時間好靜<br />\n比個無恥政府做返d野，之後爆得重大，大家應該有印象<br />\n<br />\n612 721 831  101 1111，唔會令人忘記<br />\n民怨係會埋藏係心入面，隨時爆發"},{"pid":"e829e32f8939284eb31bb2077a2a806e6226cfeb","tid":1758282,"uid":1477,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T03:09:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QWeEy2B.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQWeEy2B.png&h=90138a27&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fgsiPAW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfgsiPAW.png&h=78ef3435&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n怕香港人善忘嘅，推行動post 啦<br />\n想聲援理大手足嘅，推行動post 啦<br />\n和理非嘅，推行動post 啦<br />\n勇武嘅，推行動 post 啦<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n呢個係行動post，星期三晚，我地聚首商場，以和理非聲援理大手足<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1756593\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1756593</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"3b542d045f8ea0e71a4c43236d59af48ef7fe125","tid":1758282,"uid":24980,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T03:10:11.000Z","msg":"到時真係成班人叫獨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n谷下谷下，係咪777既暗黑兵法"},{"pid":"6bd8be83fa09c6a2421acd3937539089eed5ae3f","tid":1758282,"uid":46746,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T03:11:10.000Z","msg":"同意 林鄭真係港獨之母 反共第一人<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb4b83f0cbdf4cb7a194aae237bba8de978c9a06","tid":1758282,"uid":24980,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6bd8be83fa09c6a2421acd3937539089eed5ae3f","tid":1758282,"uid":46746,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T03:11:10.000Z","msg":"同意 林鄭真係港獨之母 反共第一人<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T03:14:10.000Z","msg":"政府係真蠢，<br />\n定係林鄭係大智若愚，<br />\n無人睇得明<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b413c3304fcd27a47831e7e189f773f8a552cfa3","tid":1758282,"uid":78574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T03:15:10.000Z","msg":"哪裡有壓逼 哪裡有反抗"},{"pid":"f58d15508e6493e2cbf430bd321d0b73b42249e2","tid":1758282,"uid":340796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T03:15:50.000Z","msg":"釋出善意: 成立獨立<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">檢討</span></span>委員會<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d5792e7c9730f7c0fdfa9f68c56053b333fc96d8","tid":1758282,"uid":268094,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T03:16:36.000Z","msg":"所以咪軟番<br />\n但班popo一定忍唔住<br />\n成班下半身諗嘢<br />\n打條太扮斯文"},{"pid":"6b86383a7f8687786be6759399fc84a423ea9bff","tid":1758282,"uid":290443,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f58d15508e6493e2cbf430bd321d0b73b42249e2","tid":1758282,"uid":340796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T03:15:50.000Z","msg":"釋出善意: 成立獨立<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">檢討</span></span>委員會<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"